{"tid":1033884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南極首次拍到罕見全黑企鵝 左膠呼籲捕食獸不要針對黑企鵝","createTime":"2019-02-23T13:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T15:06:12.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f388b0c4b8ca8092a5be960de4a0d70bcf7dd8e3","tid":1033884,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"英國廣播公司（BBC）紀錄片《王朝》（Dynasties）的拍攝團隊，近日公布在南極洲一個皇帝企鵝棲身地，拍到一隻罕見的全黑皇帝企鵝。該隻企鵝與同伴站在一起取暖，BBC表示可能是首次拍到有全黑的皇帝企鵝。<br />\n<br />\nBBC指出，一般成年皇帝企鵝（Emperor Penguin）背部呈灰黑色，肚子全白色、而頭部、尾部及蹼面都呈黑色。至於他們的臉頰及頸部有黃斑，而鳥喙的下端呈橙黃色。由片段可見，這隻罕有的企鵝沒有白色肚子，牠幾近全身黑色，只有鳥喙的下端仍保持著橙黃色。<br />\nBBC表示，這可能是首次拍到全黑皇帝企鵝，又形容牠「看似健康」，在尋找同伴並擠在一起取暖。<br />\n牠有這樣獨特的外表，是因為出現基因突變，患上了「黑變病」（Melanism）。黑變病是一種皮膚病，黑色素會在皮膚過度沉著，是動物界常見的基因突變現象。類似的現象曾經發現在國王企鵝（King Penguin）身上，但很少會在皇帝企鵝上出現。<br />\n片段亦提到，「他/她可能是這品種的唯一一隻」。受基因突變影響，牠可能很難生存至成年。牠身上的全黑色彩令牠更易吸引捕食者，例如殺人鯨或豹斑海豹。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190223/1522728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190223%2F1522728&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1EuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=4c736f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190223%2F1522728&h=000f6313\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190223/1522728</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190223/640_b1371e1a39544ab94116e0466e92a7a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190223%2F640_b1371e1a39544ab94116e0466e92a7a6.jpg&h=e17f9ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlack Lives Matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d5fc0e0755f95b1a7cc006b9b3eb9a8f95ff7f","tid":1033884,"uid":206594,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊撚度左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊撚度呼籲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6282b96e6de9fd090b2dd8cf281bee1f66324e","tid":1033884,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"全黑咪仲型"},{"pid":"1c5f27c2ecbb14f2a26d843f6f2fed0fe7dd0aa7","tid":1033884,"uid":119591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b6282b96e6de9fd090b2dd8cf281bee1f66324e","tid":1033884,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"全黑咪仲型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"但個個都白得你黑就=柒"},{"pid":"53b1d7f11b112255108d334779d1b8504689de8c","tid":1033884,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d5fc0e0755f95b1a7cc006b9b3eb9a8f95ff7f","tid":1033884,"uid":206594,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊撚度左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊撚度呼籲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n一路睇一路scan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52717ec7c3b9d3734b973f871168acdd54d5cbb","tid":1033884,"uid":96743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"Niggaguin"},{"pid":"68fed117aea84f5af876064e043ca9135a57dbf0","tid":1033884,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.vix.com/es/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/btg/curiosidades.batanga.com/files/Que-es-el-melanismo-8-animales-negros-9.jpg?itok=yEjABMfh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.vix.com%2Fes%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2Fbtg%2Fcuriosidades.batan